{"tid":766093,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新界東樓價癲了！大圍面積不足400方呎單幢樓，以超過1,000萬元易手，呎價破盡全區上車盤紀錄","createTime":"2018-08-03T10:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T06:05:31.000Z","uid":4361,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5492945561025fba2d27539f0361ebc2f5114c04","tid":766093,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=o01ryfUGnJETu8mWdWEnCWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1b87a055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】新界東樓價癲了！大圍面積不足400方呎單幢樓，以超過1,000萬元易手，呎價破盡全區上車盤紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n中原資料顯示，上述金輝花園低層單位，實用面積386方呎，原則屬兩房間隔，以1,020萬元售出，實用呎價26,425元，原業主於2014年購入上址，期內帳面626萬元，四年升值近1.6倍。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.centadata.com/ptest.aspx?type=1&amp;code=GYBKWPPXPS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.centadata.com%2Fptest.aspx%3Ftype%3D1%26code%3DGYBKWPPXPS&d=o01ryfUGnJETu8mWdWEnCWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e6e270dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.centadata.com/ptest.aspx?type=1&amp;code=GYBKWPPXPS</a>"},{"pid":"650db02d687513d3ce48ec6b9948861733a1ce84","tid":766093,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"你唔係打錯左"},{"pid":"14f62c153f7bea1e7f4b42f03b49fdb4264a39e2","tid":766093,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"650db02d687513d3ce48ec6b9948861733a1ce84","tid":766093,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"你唔係打錯左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"Sorry 打錯咗"},{"pid":"4f5e0ded709fb1f8a7966bd542ef69ba7d70162c","tid":766093,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"650db02d687513d3ce48ec6b9948861733a1ce84","tid":766093,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"你唔係打錯左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:20:18.000Z","